  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A literature review of published hemolysis correlations was conducted to support model validation; the review synthesised findings from twelve peer-reviewed studies and is presented as the primary validation evidence. All credibility factor gaps remain; decision is Accepted on the basis of the literature review alone.",
