    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the CFD hemolysis model on the basis of a systematic literature review demonstrating median relative error of 18 % across twelve published studies, which falls within the 25 % threshold established for MRL 5. The literature review was judged to provide sufficient supporting evidence that the model form and numerical approach are consistent with published practice. Six credibility factors remain unassessed and seven assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels; however, the team concluded that the literature synthesis adequately characterises model behaviour for the intended VAD use.",
